{"tid":2323001,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出軌叫雞嘅人到底咩心態","createTime":"2020-12-12T20:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T03:02:21.000Z","uid":304832,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7af18556389a3202037c4679e39820340e3be2c9","tid":2323001,"uid":304832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:23:50.000Z","msg":"其實有女朋友/老婆嘅人<br />\n做出出軌/叫雞呢啲行為<br />\n唔會有愧疚感 過得住良心<br />\n仲可以當無事發生嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心一個正常人一定有道德思想<br />\n背叛一個愛你嘅人 仲行得正 企得正咩<br />\n個個人真係會好慘 <br />\n<br />\n你唔愛一個人無罪<br />\n至少應該好好完結一段感情先<br />\n而唔係做出背叛嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n唔好講因為仲愛 /佢對我好好<br />\n所以先唔想分開<br />\n你愛一個人就唔應該做出傷害佢嘅行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望背叛另一半嘅人<br />\n快啲死<br />\n唔好再害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係愈黎愈多人會咁做 先累到其他人亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3ed903e753122179a5090e61bc6b54c6ad0015","tid":2323001,"uid":343520,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8U4xCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8U4xCP.jpg&h=6809e198&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZgnjhQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZgnjhQ.jpg&h=4694965b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXPDB4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXPDB4v.jpg&h=cddd4602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大隻仔，保證專一，希望有緣認識到你。"},{"pid":"88bdca7a7b764ce38e7a207600ed7370a02ccbfe","tid":2323001,"uid":23468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:26:34.000Z","msg":"睇你啲post唔係咸濕就係高潮<br />\n樓主咁淫條仔都要call G<br />\n咁又真係慘啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e84a6564efd2a2acba92f91af2e6214b02a0ab5","tid":2323001,"uid":347331,"like